            <thetext>The demobrowser supports URL ancors, both for categories as well as specific 
demos:

http://demo.qooxdoo.org/devel/demobrowser/index.html#mobile

http://demo.qooxdoo.org/devel/demobrowser/index.html#data~Finder.html

But it is not entirely easy to get to these URLs: For specific demos, you have 
to load the demo; then you can copy the URL from the browser location bar. For 
categories, there is no way at all to get to a copy-able URL. You just have to 
construct it by hand, e.g. by appending #&lt;category_name&gt; at the index URL.

It would be nice to have an easy way to get to these URLs. Maybe a context menu 
in the tree view with a &quot;Show URL&quot; entry could be devised?!</thetext>
          </long_desc>
